storyInfo:
Dur-nar points out one of Gummy's strange habits when attacking. Gummy tries to overcome it, but fails.
Her habits are all left by past trauma, and may take a bit of time to fade.

attributes.content: Gummy is the second one in her dorm to wake up every morning. And she has a habit.
As soon as Istina wakes her, they share a handshake. Gummy then goes next door to wake Zima in the same fashion.
Whether 'The General' decides to shake her hand or not depends entirely on her mood.
Rhodes Island Dormitories - Istina and Gummy's Room
(But she sure is taking her time today. Maybe she's been working too hard?)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (But I'm gonna be late if I keep waiting for her. C'mon, Gummy, just get up already!)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: What happened to my night light?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Weird... Did she head out already?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I guess she had something important to do.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: 'Gummy, we went out. Won't be back until evening. Please look after yourself.'
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Hmph! Look at them treating me like a kid again. Of course I can take care of myself!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: That means Zima's already up too.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Oops, I better hurry up and report in or I'm gonna be late.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Just gotta grab my trusty shield and frying pan...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I left in a hurry this morning and didn't have time to fill up my tummy.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: But I guess I should focus on work first and grab some food afterwards.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Order up! Ready for the counter!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Gotta do a shchi next? Okay, I'll have it right out!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Food's ready! Please take it to the dining area!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Next up is... Mhm, we got another fried pelmeni.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Just need someone to take this order, then I crank out the pelmeni and I'm good to go.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Gummy, I have my hands full over here! Put that out for me?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I got this. It's way lighter than my shield.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Why is everyone in such a hurry today? I turn my head for a second and she's gone...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Oh well, guess I'll just ask where to put it.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: It's gotta go around here somewhere. The lady at the cash register, that's... Gitano, right?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Why are you out here with your frying pan? Do you need my help?
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: Just one thing. Could you tell me where to put the shchi? It's getting cold!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Shchi, huh? If I recall correctly, it goes there in the middle, where Courier is standing.
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: Are you sure you don't need any help, Little Cub?
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: I'm perfectly fine! See you later, Gitano!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Forget it. You couldn't lift it anyway.
attributes.name: Spot

attributes.content: Welcome, what can I get for you?
attributes.name: Courier

attributes.content: Braised pork and vegetables? Coming right up. And a steamed egg with your stir-fried vegetables? No problem.
attributes.name: Courier

attributes.content: Sorry to bother you, Gummy, but would you mind taking this pot back to the kitchen?
attributes.name: Courier

attributes.content: You've really outdone yourself, Gummy. C'mere, I have a cookie for you. You must be hungry, right?
attributes.name: Courier

attributes.content: It's my pleasure. Make sure to have a proper meal after this, all right?
attributes.name: Courier

attributes.content: See you later, Gitano. I need to head back and get some stuff done.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (Just hold out a bit longer... It's almost time to eat!)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Wooaahh! Kay, you can't go in there!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You can't! Don't you see the sign on the door?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I see a red circle with a tilty red line going through it.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: That means 'Kay is not allowed in here.' Got it?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: If you get it, why are you still going in?!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: If you're hungry, you can just get in line and order something to eat.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Y- You're not allowed in there!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Fine, fine! I'll think of something!!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: If I give you this cookie, will you promise not to go inside?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: There's... there's still... one more to go...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Just hold on... just a little longer!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I can't even scoop up the food......
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I can't do this anymore. I have to eat something!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Gummy has a habit. When she's famished, something takes hold of her,
And she can't resist her urge to eat...
So soft... Mmmhh.... It must be delicious.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Gummy, why are you chewing on my hip?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (Gummy is practically inhaling the bread in her hands...)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (...washing it down with a swig of soup.)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: C-calm down, Gummy, the food's not going anywhere. And we got training in the afternoon, y'know.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (She doesn't leave a single scrap on her plate...)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (...and doesn't hesitate to reach for seconds.)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (In no time, she's gobbled up an entire table full of food.)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I'll get back to you later.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Whew. I feel like a whole new Gummy!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Instructor, don't you want to eat?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Sure do. But somehow all the food I brought out disappeared into your belly.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Don't worry about it, I can always get more.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: By the way, how'd you end up so hungry? You skip breakfast or something?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I overslept this morning and didn't have time to eat, so...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Y'know, you might just be that type of girl. With a bottomless pit for a stomach.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Yup, just like that one over there.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Kay? She's charging the kitchen again?! I better
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Relax, we got someone keeping an eye on her. Plus, they laid out some goodies near the door just in case she gets in. She won't make it to anything important.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Oh, I thought those were welcome baskets for new recruits...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Yeah that too. Whatever gets the job done.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If we sealed that door, it'd hurt her feelings. Letting her in every now and then lets her feel like she won. And it doesn't cost us much.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Um, so who's in charge of keeping an eye on her?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Good choice. She's always got it together.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: That reminds me, I have to ask you something. It has to do with training.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I notice you have trouble moving your arms, especially in quick, repetitive motions. Why is that?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I've watched you in combat, and it's the same in the kitchen. You get two good strokes in and then you have to stop.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Huh? Well, that's a bad habit if I ever saw one. Can we fix it?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Because stopping like that on the battlefield is gonna get you killed.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: But if we can cure you, I'm sure you've got the next Rhodes Island Chopping Competition in the bag.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Good. We'll get to it after defender practice.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: We won't know if we can fix that habit until we try.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Rhode Island Training Center - Defender Training Room
Last round of the day. Let's power through.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I want four sets of planks, time
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Okay, we're done. Go cool off.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You ready? What we talked about at lunch?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I'll get the training shield, and you can use your weapon there.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Now relax. That's gonna be an important part of your rehab.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Okay, Gummy. I want you to hit me as hard as you can.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I know you're tired from afternoon training, but it's actually the perfect time to work on this.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Great. Now gimme whatever's left in the tank.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (If it's a conditioned reflex, that should have shaken out some more swings.)
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Gummy is a good cook, but she has a habit.
She chops only twice. Should she ever chop a third time
She'll chop straight through the cutting board, right into the counter itself.
I'm fine, I'm fine. It's just been a long time since I took a hit like that.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Is this another one of your 'habits'?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Relax. I told you, I'm fine.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: But it looks like this problem of yours is more complicated than I thought.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: On your third swing, you subconsciously put your full strength into it. Is that right?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: And I'm guessing that takes a fourth swing off the table.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If we were in the kitchen just now, you'd've chopped that cutting board into a nice, clean pair.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Here I thought we just had to push you over the edge... Turns out there's something else going on here.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I jumped headfirst into this without really feeling it out. Sorry, Gummy.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: It's my fault for being a lousy student.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Let's call it for today. You go home and rest up. Give me some time to noodle on this.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: But if you want to try again, you know where to find me.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (Those Ursus Youth Scouts are stupid strong.)
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (I better pay Gavial a visit in Medical.)
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (I'll grab her something to eat on the way.)
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Rhodes Island Dormitories - Zima, Istina, and Gummy's Quarters
She does not turn on the lights.
She hangs her 'shield' in the corner,
She wants to do better, for everyone who does so much to help her.
Since coming to Rhodes Island, Gummy's 'habits' only bred more habits.
And she knows those habits bother the people around her.
She can do nothing but keep on being 'Gummy.'
She carries a safe door and a frying pan with her everywhere she goes.
She uses the entire tube of toothpaste, going so far as to suck out the last few drops.
When up somewhere high, she keeps far away from the edge, even if there's a guardrail.
When she's famished, she has to fight the urge to devour the nearest object. Should she fail...
If she finds herself in the dark too long...
Oh, Gummy, you're back? Why didn't you turn on the lights?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: All her myriad habits dissipate as soon as she sees Zima and Istina.
No doubt she was sniveling alone in the corner after something shook her.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: What am I gonna do with you?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Gummy, start cleaning. Leto is coming.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: There. Give Istina back her handkerchief after you wash it.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Get to work, Gummy. I did the shopping. The rest is up to you two.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Okay. What's so special about today anyway?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: It's been exactly one year since we came to Rhodes Island. Zima even woke up early for the occasion. If you believe it.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Phew I'm beat. I'm gonna lay down for a bit. Call me when Leto gets here.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Oh no you're not. There's too much to be done.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: I'll go prepare the refreshments. You're responsible for getting Zima up.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Spare me the schmaltz. I'm sleepy.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Good. Now put her to work. I have my hands full.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Ugh. I just carried all those bags. Why do I have to work more?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Call it the burden of command.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Come on in and give me a hand.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: What're you standing around for? Get busy.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: It's a laugh from the very depths of her soul.
And she wants everyone to share such a laugh.
(It's been a long time since we all got together.)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (I hope Rosa can come next time.)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I ate your cookie earlier, so I got you a new one.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Vulcan taught me how to make it. It's fresh outta the oven.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Hurry up and eat it before it gets cold.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Nichego sebe, that's one hell of a cookie.
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Rhodes Island Dormitories - Zima, Istina, and Gummy's Quarters
Phew. That was great. But now it's bedtime.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Just need my trusty night light...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Now that I think of it, it wasn't on this morning either.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: She absolutely must sleep with a night light.
Can I sleep with you tonight?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Are you sleeping with us too?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Can the three of us really fit in Gummy's bed?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Guess we're making a Gummy bear sandwich.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: All right. Just tell me if it gets too hot and stuffy. I'll go back to my room.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I'm turning out the lights. Good night.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: When was the last time we all slept together like this?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I can't even remember. I don't even want to remember.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Forget I asked. Just get some sleep.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: As soon as her head hits the pillow, huh?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Guess I'm the only one who doesn't pass right out.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Settle down, brain. We got a busy day tomorrow. Ugh.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You know the Ursus Student Self-Governing Group?
They're the habit Gummy just can't quit.
